{"lemma":"أَرْنَبَةٍ","slug":"أَرْنَبَةٍ","root":"#.ر.ن.ب","root_slug":"_-ر-ن-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ر-ن-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16761"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rabbit (mammal)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"1 million EGP","tags":["Egypt","dated","slang"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ʔarnab-. Compare Hebrew אַרְנָב (ʾarnā́ḇ)."},"ipa":["/ʔar.nab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16761","headword_ar":"اَرْنَبَةٌ","root":"rnb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lobule,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the nose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, A, K:) this is [also] called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aronabapu AlA^anofi","text_ar":"اَرْنَبَةُ الاَنْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb:) it is one of the parts that touch the ground in prostration [in prayer]: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAnibu","text_ar":"اَرَانِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, A, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadaEa A^aronabatahu","text_ar":"جَدَعَ اَرْنَبَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut off the end of his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he held him in mean estimation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in contempt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadotuhumo mujad~aEiY","text_ar":"وَجَدْتُهُمْ مُجَدَّعِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^araAnibi A^a$ad~a fazaEFA mina AlA^araAnibi","text_ar":"الاَرَانِبِ اَشَدَّ فَزَعًا مِنَ الاَرَانِبِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found them to be held in contempt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the ends of their noses cut off,"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more fearful than hares"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aronabN","text_ar":"اَرْنَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","S","A","K","Mgh","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}